OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStorm Dave
OL,6,Fwill bring gales this evening with
OL,7,Fsome heavy and blustery spells of
OL,8,Frain. The storm will clear in the
OL,9,Fearly hours and winds will ease.
OL,10,FTurning mostly dry by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,13,Fshowers on Easter Day with lighter
OL,14,Fwinds. Feeling colder than previous
OL,15,Fdays with a fresh breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
