OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fon Monday and Tuesday with good sunny
OL,7,Fspells and turning increasingly warm.
OL,8,FSkies clouding over with some showers
OL,9,Fpossible on Wednesday, and turning
OL,10,Fless warm.
